<title>USA: TABLE - Reader's Digest cuts qtly dividend.</title>
<headline>TABLE - Reader's Digest cuts qtly dividend.</headline>
<dateline>PLEASANTVILLE, N.Y. 1997-07-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Quarterly</p>
<p>			  Latest		    Prior</p>
<p> Amount		 $0.225		     $0.45</p>
<p> Pay		    Aug. 5</p>
<p> Record		July 24</p>
<p>Note: Full name of company is Reader's Digest Association Inc.</p>
<p>The company said the dividend change allows it to preserve cash to fund investment in the &quot;strategic growth program&quot; announced in April.</p>
<p>On April 23, the company announced it would spend $400 million over four years in more aggressive publishing and promotion initiatives.</p>
